≥0⇒↥≥0 : ∀ {n dm} → mkℚᵘ n dm ≥ 0ℚᵘ → n ℤ.≥ 0ℤ
≥0⇒↥≥0 {n} {dm} r≥0 = ℤ.≤-trans (drop-*≤* r≥0)
                                (ℤ.≤-reflexive $ ℤ.*-identityʳ n)

>0⇒↥>0 : ∀ {n dm} → mkℚᵘ n dm > 0ℚᵘ → n ℤ.> 0ℤ
>0⇒↥>0 {n} {dm} r>0 = ℤ.<-≤-trans (drop-*<* r>0)
